title: [1508521049] Catching Wild Catfish By Hand in Oklahoma - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon meets local champion Lee McFarlane, and is taught the way of noodle fishing to catch some catfish in a tricky Oklahoma lake.
From Gordon Ramsay's The F Word
